HEADWORD: Leave-taking
<hw>Leave"-tak`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Taking of
leave; the act of departing politely; the giving of parting
compliments.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> farewell, leave, parting.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

